るラノワール、憤怒であり平安。_#','#_"Minha mente é a cobertura das copas. Meu coração é o abraço das raízes. Eu sou a eterna Llanowar, sua fúria e sua paz."_#','#_"Разум мой простирается лесным пологом. Сердце мое бьется в сплетении корней. Я - бессмертный Лановар, его неистовство и покой"._#','#_"Mi mente es la expansión de la enramada. Mi corazón es el abrazo de las raíces. Soy el inmortal Llanowar, su furia y su paz."_#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('135259','Mortal Combat','10E','Enchantment','R','{2}{B}{B}','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'At the beginning of your upkeep, if twenty or more creature cards are in your graveyard, you win the game.','#_The crowd roared, the fighters bled, and the dead piled high in the pits. Only the Cabal could win._#',NULL,'Mike Ploog','160','4','£7/15/2007: If you don’t have twenty or more creature cards in your graveyard by the time your upkeep starts, the ability won’t trigger that turn.£7/15/2007: Mortal Combat’s ability has an “intervening ‘if’ clause,” so the condition is checked again when the triggered ability resolves. If you don’t still have twenty creature cards in your graveyard, the ability does nothing.','B',NULL,'0.35','0.86','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'B','杀戮争战','殺戮爭戰','Combat mortel','Auf Leben und Tod','Combattimento Mortale','死闘','Combate Mortal','Смертный Бой','Combate mortal',NULL,'结界','結界','Enchantement','Verzauberung','Incantesimo','エンチャント','Encantamento','Чары','Encantamiento',NULL,'在你的维持开始时，若你的坟墓场中有二十或更多张生物牌，你便赢得此盘游戏。','在你的維持開始時，若你的墳墓場中有二十或更多張生物牌，你便贏得此盤遊戲。','Au début de votre entretien, s''il y a au moins vingt cartes de créature dans votre cimetière, vous gagnez la partie.','Falls zu Beginn deines Versorgungssegments zwanzig oder mehr Kreaturenkarten in deinem Friedhof sind, gewinnst du das Spiel.','All''inizio del tuo mantenimento, se ci sono venti o più carte creatura nel tuo cimitero, vinci la partita.','あなたのアップキープの開始時に、あなたの墓地に20枚以上のクリーチャー・カードがある場合、あなたはこのゲームに勝利する。','No início de sua manutençã